  "Description": {
    "English": "Wafer-thin lens arrays are arranged in a highly calibrated matrix, focusing the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Mining Beam</span> on an atomic level.<br><br>This extra precision allows for highly efficient mining. Elements are extracted more efficiently, <span class=\"name name-stellar\">increasing the yield</span> from items harvested with the Multi-Tool.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "薄片厚度的透镜阵列排列于高度校准的矩阵中，把<span class=\"name name-technology\">开采光束</span>的聚焦提升至原子层级。<br><br>这种额外的精度让高效开采成为可能，进而提升元素提取效率，使用多用途工具收获物品时<span class=\"name name-stellar\">增加产出</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "極薄的透鏡排列成精心調校的矩陣，讓<span class=\"name name-technology\">採礦光束</span>在原子尺度下亦可精準聚焦。<br><br>如此精準度，可大幅提升採礦效率。元素萃取效率更高，工具組採集道具時<span class=\"name name-stellar\">產量也更高</span>。"
  },
